          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/148491752/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u148491752-1.jpg" alt="吃吃痴呀！停停" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/40060639/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/40060639/" class="">一</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/148491752/" class=" " title="吃吃痴呀！停停">吃吃痴呀！停停</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="40060639">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">“学与教为先，政治次之，著述乃其余事”序言里写，这是钱穆为普通读者写的书，然而考证详尽细致，也一点不得马虎。直观体验儒家风格可看此书，钱穆填的词徘徊而挥之不去“手空空无一物，路遥遥无止尽”，而“艰难我奋进，困乏我多情”。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-11-06 17:56</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                “学与教为先，政治次之，著述乃其余事”序言里写，这是钱穆为普通读者写的书，然而考证详尽细致，也一点不得马虎。直观体验儒家风格可看此书，钱穆填的词徘徊而挥之不去“手空空无一物，路遥遥无止尽”，而“艰难我奋进，困乏我多情”。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
